QuestData.Title: King of the Hill
QuestData.Description:
Loksey is ready. It is finally time to begin the hunt.
Take him to Wanecrypt. The Fearstalker and the other hunters will be there already.
Hurry now. She does not like to be kept waiting.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Houndmaster Loksey to the Fearstalker in Wanecrypt Hill.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak to the Fearstalker at Wanecrypt Hill.

Objectives.Objective: Houndmaster Loksey delivered to Wanecrypt Hill
